actions.text: Referred to House Committee on Appropriations.

official_title: Resolution disapproving the deferral of certain budge authority (D76-71) relating to the Department of Agriculture, Commodity Credit Corporation, which is proposed by the President in his message of November 29, 1975, transmitted under section 1013 of the Impoundment Control Act of 1974.

summary.text: Disapproves the deferral of budget authority (D76-71) relating to the Department of Agriculture, Commodity Credit Corporation, which is proposed by the President in his message of November 29, 1975, transmitted under the Impoundment Control Act of 1974.
